OL,3,CMayor must apologise to sacked bus
OL,4,Cdriver, London Assembly demands
OL,6,FThe London Assembly has demanded that
OL,7,Fthe Mayor of London, Sir Sadiq Khan,
OL,8,Fapologises over the sacking of a bus
OL,9,Fdriver who chased down a thief to
OL,10,Freturn a passengers stolen necklace.
OL,12,FThe bus driver, Mark Hehir, was
OL,13,Fbranded a "hero" by the assembly
OL,14,Fmembers. On Thursday, they passed a
OL,15,Funanimous motion calling for an
OL,16,Finvestigation into his dismissal.
