OL,3,CMayor must apologise to sacked bus
OL,4,Cdriver, London Assembly demands
OL,6,FThe motion called for Sir Sadiq Khan
OL,7,Fand Transport for London to "apply
OL,8,Fpressure to Metroline to reinstate
OL,9,FMark or provide appropriate
OL,10,Fcompensation", and to "set out clear
OL,11,Fguidance for transport workers
OL,12,Fprotecting passengers."
OL,14,FMark was fired by Metroline after he
OL,15,Fchased a thief who stole a passenger's
OL,16,Fnecklace and punched them- which he
OL,17,Fsays was in self-defence.
OL,19,FThe vote comes after Mark said it was
OL,20,F"disappointing" that the mayor had
OL,21,Fbeen silent on the matter.
