OL,3,CMayor must apologise to sacked bus
OL,4,Cdriver, London Assembly demands
OL,6,FThe motion was brough forward by
OL,7,FLondon Assembly member, Keith Prince.
OL,8,FHe said:
OL,10,F"This is not about encouraging
OL,11,Freckless behaviour.
OL,13,F"It is about whether we are
OL,14,Fcomfortable with a system that
OL,15,Fpunishes frontline workers for
OL,16,Fstepping in when crime happens right
OL,17,Fin front of them.
