OL,3,CMayor must apologise to sacked bus
OL,4,Cdriver, London Assembly demands
OL,6,F"By supporting this motion
OL,7,Funanimously, the Assembly has sent a
OL,8,Fclear message that public concern,
OL,9,Fcommon sense, and fairness still
OL,10,Fmatter."
OL,12,FMark spoke to ITV News London earlier
OL,13,Fthis week.
OL,15,FEarlier this week shadow justice
OL,16,Fminister Dr Kieran Mullan, shadow
OL,17,Ftransport minister Richard Holden and
OL,18,FMs Hall wrote to Sir Khan to demand
OL,19,F"serious consideration of
OL,20,Freinstatement or appropriate
OL,21,Fcompensation."
