OL,3,CMayor must apologise to sacked bus
OL,4,Cdriver, London Assembly demands
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London will have to
OL,7,Fformally respond to the assembly but
OL,8,Fdoes not have to accept the
OL,9,Frecommendations to reinstate Mr Hehir
OL,10,Fand provide compensation.
OL,12,FMore than 135,000 people have signed a
OL,13,Fpetition in support of the bus driver,
OL,14,Fwhich was launched after an employment
OL,15,Ftribunal upheld Metroline's decision
OL,16,Fto sack the bus drive and more than
OL,17,F#40,000 has been raised for the former
OL,18,Fbus driver.
